          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你前去问来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，黑汉，我大王问你，家乡哪里，姓甚名谁？对我讲了，我好去禀我大王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四喽兵",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，禀大王……"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，先将你强盗名姓讲来。我便言俺的家乡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦？你要问我大王姓名。你们退下了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四喽兵",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四喽兵同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我讲来你听。我大王乃湖广房州人氏，父名纪德，自幼在此落草。父母亡故，"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她便作了大王。我的话说完了，请你讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，站开些。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，我就站开些。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，且住。他乃绿林中人，俺就通了名性，料也无妨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，站过来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "提起俺的威名，只恐吓破你们苦胆。你且听了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家住绛州龙门县，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "迁移长安御驾前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "跨海征东十二年。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父讳丁山掌兵权。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "猛、勇、刚、强世袭官。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "英雄无敌天下传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祖父白袍薛仁贵"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "镇国一品樊氏母"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "所生弟兄人四个"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺名薛刚通城虎"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是、是、是，我明白了。待我禀过大王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "问来没有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "问来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么名姓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "提起威名，吓破你的苦胆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "讲来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他乃绛州龙门人氏，先祖薛仁贵，父名丁山，母亲樊氏，镇国夫人，兄弟四个，"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "猛、勇、刚、强，世袭王爵。他名薛刚，混号通城虎。大王你怕不怕？"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是天意随人愿，"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "月老匹配美姻缘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，将军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "急忙松绑陪笑脸"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "军卒无知犯尊颜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爵主请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喽啰无知，望乞恕罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问爵主，不在长安，为何路过荒山？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只为正月十五夜，大闹花灯，踢死殿下，惊坏朝廷。是我在人丛中打出，独行"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "至此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可知老王爷一家之事否？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺只顾逃走，并不知家内吉凶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，爵主，奴有一言，不好启齿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有话请讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个……"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朱唇未启红上脸，"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "羞人答答怎好言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，纪申。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你可知道吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "知道什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你大王今年一十七岁吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谁与大王作生日吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你大王尚未婚配。今见薛爵主武艺高强，若是错过，何处择选。要留他在此做"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一寨主。命你前去说来，重重赏你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "做寨主……可还有什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，附耳上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。我明白了，明白了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，爵主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恭喜恭喜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喜从何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我大王见爵主英雄，欲偕白首。今日相会，乃前世良缘，婚姻大事，不要错过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爵主料难推辞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢。哎呀，我又无栖身之地，不免允从此事，再打听爹娘吉凶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，俺无聘礼，怎好婚配？"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我禀过大王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启大王：他便允从，只是无有聘礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只要爵主允从，不用聘礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王说：只要爵主允从，不用聘礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用聘礼，请你大王近前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请大王近前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，将军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "承蒙夫人不弃，只是即要差人打听我家的吉凶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "件件依从。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请大王夫人下面更衣，好拜花烛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "男英女杰岂寻常，"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪鸾英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姻缘千里隔家乡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日婚配偕白首，"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来年生个小大王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，有赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢大王。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
